creator: Fergus Software Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Manage all of your jobs from the palm of your hand with our NEW mobile app - Fergus Go.

The simple design and powerful functionality of Fergus Go allows you to navigate through all of your upcoming jobs and complete all the job admin you need to complete while you’re on the job or on the road.

- Record, log and view timesheets easier than ever before
- Easily find or add notes and photos against jobs they belong to
- View or complete checklists
- See upcoming jobs for the day, week or month.
- Communicate with someone, or everyone in the team, in one place.
- Find any of the jobs in your business in a couple of taps
- Stay in the loop with updates on jobs

title:

1.31.1

creator: Fergus Software Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Fergus: The Ultimate Tradie App & Job Management Software for trades businesses.

Fergus is the all-in-one job management software designed to make life easier for tradies. Whether it’s quoting, invoicing, scheduling, or team management, Fergus has everything you need to keep your business running smoothly. Manage jobs, track time, control costs, and stay compliant with safety forms like SWMS—Fergus has tradies covered.

Save Time with Automated Tradie Software
Fergus integrates with over 100 suppliers, letting you automatically import invoices and match them to the correct jobs. Never miss charging out costs with supplier integration. Sync with your accounting software to update contacts, invoices, and payments automatically, so you can focus on what matters.

Trusted by Tradies
“Fergus is the best job management software for tradies.”
“Fergus is the ultimate tradie app.”

Perfect for Any Tradie Business
Over 20,000 tradies rely on Fergus to manage their jobs. Whether you're a solo operator or managing a team of 60+, Fergus helps you succeed. It’s the ideal job management software for a range of trades, including:
Plumbers
Electricians
HVAC Technicians
Roofers
Builders
And more!

What Fergus Can Do for You
Complete Job Tracking: Instantly access customer info, job files, photos, notes, and scheduling on your mobile, tablet, or desktop.
Quick Quotes & Invoices: Generate accurate quotes, access supplier price books, and invoice efficiently. Get paid faster!
Team Management: Keep everyone on the same page with real-time updates. Track time and materials, and stay organised with the Fergus mobile app.

Support When You Need It
Get free support via email, chat, or phone, plus access to our Help Centre with tutorials and articles. Our partner services will help you get set up and running in no time.

Download Fergus Today
Start saving time on job management, invoicing, and admin tasks with Fergus—the job management software made for tradies. Focus on the work that matters!
